Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,037 利用VisualStateManager来创建自适应的触发器 （翻译 by Elenore）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好，我是Bob Tabor\NHi, I'm Bob Tabor with
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,来自 www.LearnVisualStudio.net\Nwww.LearnVisualStudio.net, and I want you to take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们先看一下屏幕\Non-screen right now because
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.17,0:00:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我要展示一下效果\NI wanted to illustrate an idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.08,0:00:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这样你们更好理解\Nit's easier to show you than explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个简单的应用，只用了一个网格控件\NHere I have a simple application with a Grid,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.71,0:00:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,把它的背景颜色设为红色\NI set the Grid's Background="Red"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我还写了一个简单的文本块\Nand I have a simple TextBlock and I've got a,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,字体大小大概是16点或者18点\NI don't know, 16 point, 18 point font there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,注意看，当我改变它的大小时发生了什么\NAnd so watch what happens though whenever I resize this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,当我把它改变到一定大小时\NI get to a certain point and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就触发了一些变化\Nit triggers the change of the BackgroundColor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,它的背景颜色变成了黄色，字体也变大了\Nto Yellow, and the FontSize to a larger FontSize,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是24点的样子\NI think like 24 or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们继续改变窗口尺寸\NNow let's continue to resize,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.14,0:00:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,背景颜色变成了蓝色\Nand the Cackground color changes to blue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.14,0:00:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,文本块的字体变的更大了\Nand I use an even larger Font for the TextBlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这些情况之所以能发生\NAnd so this is made possible by an object called
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因为我们用了一个叫 VisualStateManager 的对象\Nthe VisualStateManager and it does
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就像它的名字那样说的\Nexactly what it sounds like, it manages
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,它用来管理应用的可视化状态\Nthe visual state of your application,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,比如界面元素的位置和大小\Nwhere things belong, the sizes of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.45,0:01:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,颜色，这些都是通过你编写的触发器来实现的\Nthe colors of things based on Triggers that you create.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.22,0:01:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，基本上你可以处理任何对象的任何属性\NSo, essentially you can manipulate any property
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以改变大小、\Nof any object, you can resize,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,改变位置、设置可见性\Nreposition, set the visibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.82,0:01:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,设置字体大小、设置字体样式\Nyou can set the FontSize, set the FontFamily.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,任何你能想到的界面变化\NAnything that you possibly can imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,都是基于当前窗口大小\Nbased on the current size of the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.94,0:01:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,或当前屏幕尺寸的\Nor the current available screen real estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可以想一想这么把这些\NAnd so think about how that applies to the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.72,0:01:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,应用到 UWP 上\NUniversal Windows Platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这其中一个卖点在于\NOne of the selling points is that you're able
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,（球M$ 广告费）\N你可以只写一份基础的代码\Nto write one code base and then use it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,（球M$ 广告费）\N然后它就可以用在各种不同外形的场景下\Nacross all these different form factors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.09,0:01:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,（球M$ 广告费）\N使得你的应用可以适应\NAnd so this allows you to accommodate different
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,（球M$ 广告费）\N不同屏幕分辨率、不同尺寸的设备\Nscreen resolutions for different form factors
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,（球M$ 广告费）\N然而代码都是一样的\Nwith the same code base.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这个基本概念\NAnd so this is a very foundational concept
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我们这节课要讲的\Nand what we're going to talk about briefly in this lesson,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还会讲到这个如何应用于自适应的布局\Nwe'll talk about how this applies to adaptive layout,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,换句话说，就是基于屏幕尺寸\Nin other words, changing the entire layout
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,改变应用程序的整个布局\Nof your application based on the screen size,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:01:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,即外形因素\Nthe form factor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.42,0:02:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这个我们下个视频会讲到\NWe'll talk about that in the very next video.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,再强调一遍，这个概念可以实现都是因为\NBut again, this is all made possible because of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一个叫 VisualStateManager 的对象\Na object called the VisualStateManager,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你要创建一个VisualStateGroup，然后在其中\NYou create a VisualStateGroup and inside of that group
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,创建一组状态（State）\Nyou create a series of States.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你要给状态命名\NSo a State can be anything, you give it a name
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还要写一些触发器\Nand you give it some Triggers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们来看一下\NSo in this case take a look at
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚那个应用程序的代码\Nthe application we were just looking at.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这里我写了一个名为 PhoneVisualState 的 VisualState\NSo here I have a VisualState that I called Phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,和一个叫 TabletVisualState 的 VisualState\NI have another VisualState that I called Tablet,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,or VisualStateTablet,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个状态\NAnd then another VisualState
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,叫VisualStateDesktop\Nthat I called VisualStateDesktop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以按自己喜好命名\NNow you can name these things anything you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道有没有标准大小\NAnd I don't know if there's any standard sizes or
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,或者其它让你觉得为难的地方\Nanything that you've got to stick with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,它都是有意义的\NIt's whatever makes sense for your application,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我觉得\Nand that's why I think, you know, testing your application
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,需要不停地在不同的设备上测试你的应用程序\Ncontinually on different devices, and VisualStudio
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,而显然， Visual Studio 让这件事变得简单\Nobviously makes that very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在尽可能多的不同外形的场景下测试\NBut testing it as many different form factors as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,会帮助你得到最佳的布局效果\Nwill help you see the optimal layout
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在不同的外形场景下\Nfor that given form factor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好哒我们来看看代码\NSo here we go, we have a VisualState.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:03:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一个 VisualState 包含两个东西\NAnd a VisualState is comprised of two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一个是一组触发器\NFirst of all, a series of Triggers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一组 Setters\Nand then a series of Setters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种情况下，触发器本质上是\NSo when a Trigger is essentially, in this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是最小窗口宽度（MinWindowWidth）\Neither the MinWindowWidth,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,还是最小窗口高度（MinWindowHeight）\Nor the MinWindowHeight,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦满足条件，就会触发\Nthat once it's achieved will Trigger
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,表现为特定的视觉状态（VisualState）\Nthis particular VisualState.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，一旦一个状态被触发了\NSo once that State is Triggered,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Setter 就起作用了\Nthen it applies these Setters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这些 Setter 很像\NAnd these Setters are very similar to the Setters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在样式中使用的 Setter ，对吧\Nthat we had in Styles right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个“Target”属性\NWhere we have a Target, property,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.49,0:03:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个叫“ColorGrid”的对象\Nso here's the object, the ColorGrid object.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把它的背景颜色设为红色\NAnd I'm going to set the Background Value="Red".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,对文本块也是一样的处理\NAlright, same thing with the TextBlock,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,用 MessageTextBlock\Nthis MessageTextBlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我用了点（.）标记，这样我们可以访问\NAnd I use the dot notation just like we would to access
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对象的成员了，这是C#的语法\Nmembers of an object in C#.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们用点操作符来访问 FontSize 属性\NSo we use the dot notation to access the property FontSize
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把它的值设为 18，当我们处于\Nand we set it's value to 18, whenever we are in that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,窗口宽度大于0的时候，因为最小窗口宽度为0\Nsmallest state where the MinWindowWidth="0".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个状态的触发器\NThe next State up has a Trigger
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,设置的最小窗口宽度是600\Nof MinWindowWidth="600".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:04:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,当满足最小窗口宽度时\NAnd at that point then we were applying,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们写的 Setters 就会\Nthe Setters that we're applying are setting the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,把 ColorGrid 的背景颜色设为黄色\Nbackground ColorGrid to yellow,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,同时文本块的字体设为36点\Nand the FontSize of the MessageTextBlock to 36.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对于桌面级的场合\NAnd then finally the desktop, as long as the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,最小窗口宽度设为800\NMinWindowWidth="800",
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦窗口宽度达到最小值\Nonce we stretch it out that far,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,应用程序的背景颜色就会\Nthen we were able to change the Background
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,变成蓝色，字体大小变为54\Nto blue and the FontSize to 54.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以从概念上讲，这个还蛮简单的\NSo conceptually it's easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,非常简单\Nit's very easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,它让你可以做很多创造性的事情\NIt allows you to get creative
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,当你想让你的应用程序发生一些变化时\Nwith how you want to make changes to your application
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就用这个工具吧（VisualStateManager）\Nusing this tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我们要讲的概念\NAnd that's really all there is to the notion of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个视频中\Nwhat we were calling in the video
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,叫做自适应触发器（AdaptiveTrigger）\Nan AdaptiveTrigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个 AdaptiveTrigger 对象\NHere's an AdaptiveTrigger object,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们写了一个触发器，然后\Nwe set the Trigger and then once that Trigger is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦这个触发器被触发，Setters 就起作用了\Nfired off, we apply the Setters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒\NOk great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我要给你看的是\NNow I wanted to show you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:05:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个工具可以帮助你来做这些\Nthat there's actually a tool that will help you do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上我并不喜欢这个工具\NNow I don't like this tool, honestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的是很诚实地告诉你哦\NI'm being completely honest with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实更喜欢自己手写\NI would prefer to do it by hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这样感觉有更多主导权\NI feel like I have more control.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果你更喜欢视觉化的操作\NBut if you're a more visual type person
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你也不记得那么多语法\Nand you don't remember the syntax
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你还不想查参考手册\Nand you don't want to look up on your cheat sheet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们等会儿会把这个加到参考手册里去\Nas we'll add this to our cheat sheet in a little bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你就可以用这个懒方法啦\Nyou can use this trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在解决方案资源管理器里，看到你的项目\NIn your project, in the Solution Explorer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以看到\Nyou can see here I have
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有一个新项目，名叫 UsingBlendForVisualStates\Na New Project called UsingBlendForVisualStates,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我还写了同样的“ColorGrid”和文本块\Nand I have the same Color Grid and TextBlock,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不过还没有添加任何东西在里面\Nbut I haven't added anything else to it just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在解决方案资源管理器里面，右击项目名\NHere in the Solution Explorer I'm going to right-click
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,选择“在 Blend 中设计”\Non the project and select Design in Blend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Blend 是一个工具\NAnd so Blend is a tool that should be installed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,随 Visual Studio 一起安装的\Nalong with Visual Studio
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,它主要是做一些设计类的工作\NAnd it really was intended for
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是通过设计来实现\Nmore design work, and by design I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,美术设计之类的工作\Naesthetic design work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以看到它和 Visual Studio\NAnd you see that it has many of the same
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多相同的功能\Nfeatures of Visual Studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,右边是属性窗口\NOn the right-hand side we have the properties window.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,解决方案资源管理器默认停靠在这里\NThere is also a Solution Explorer docked by default
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这左边\Nover here on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Blend帮你做了两件事\NThere are two things that Blend does for you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这两件事，你自己在 Visual Studio 做起来\Nthat you can't easily do
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可能不那么容易\Nin Visual Studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一件事呢\NAnd one of them, is it gives you this cool little
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就是让你优雅地创建 VisualState\Nway of creating VisualStates and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,并且记录状态的改变\Nrecording the changes in a given State.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,另一件事呢，就是动画结合起来\NAnd then secondly, working with animation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这个我们不打算在这系列讲到\Nwhich we're not going to talk about in this series.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来展示给你看 Blend 是怎么工作的吧\NBut let me show you how this works,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上它超简单\Nin fact it's just easier if I go straight
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我直接到设计界面的话\Nto the design view for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们来看看\NAnd let's go down to where we can actually see
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的设计区\Nour design area.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这是对象和时间轴窗口\NSo there's this Objects and Timeline window,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一般停靠在左边\Ntypically docked on the left-hand side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你看我可以向下展开\NAnd you can see that I can drill down and see
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,看到 ColorGrid 和它里面包含的东西\Nthe ColorGrid and whatever's inside the ColorGrid,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,一个 MessageTextBlock\Nin this case, the MessageTextBlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我要看看状态标签\NAnd then I'm going to go to the States tab here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一般停靠在左上角\Nthat's usually docked up on the upper left-hand corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我要添加一个状态组\NAnd what I'll do is, I'm going to add a state group,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我点一下这个小按钮\Nso I'm going to click this little button here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,然后它就会创建一个 VisualStateGroup\NAnd this will create a VisualStateGroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我要添加一个状态到这个状态组里\NI'm going to add a state to that group
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,将它命名为 Phone\Nd I'm going to call this state Phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以按自己想法命名\Nwe can call it anything we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要添加一个状态\NI'm going to add another state
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这个叫 Tablet\Nthat I'm going to call Tablet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要添加一个叫 Desktop 的状态\NAnd I'm going to add another state that I call Desktop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,注意到当我选择它们其中任意一个时\NAnd notice that whenever I select any of these,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这里会出现一个小红点\Nthat a little red light
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,在被选择的状态的左边\Nis selected on the left-hand side,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,同时在设计区会出现红色的边框\Nand there's a red border all around the designer area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能看到状态 Phone 就开始记录了\NYou might also see that Phone state recording is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我选择了状态 Tablet，然后状态 Tablet 就开始记录了\NNow I select Tablet and Tablet state recording is on
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以基本上你要做的就是\NSo essentially what you're doing here is,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,记录属性窗口中\Nyou're recording the changes in the property window
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要的变化\Nthat you want to be made
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在你选择的状态下\Nwhen you're in that given state.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们还有一些其他事需要做\NNow there's something else that we need to do
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们继续下去之前\Nbefore we actually continue on with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是，我们要设置触发器\NAnd that is, we need to set the Triggers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:07:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你在这里看到的\NSo as you can see here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这有一个闪电样的标志\Nthere's a little lightning bolt
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,在右边\Noff to the right-hand side
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我要点击它（编辑自适应触发器）\NI'm going to click Edit Adaptive Triggers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我要添加一个 AdaptiveTrigger\Nand I'm going to add an AdaptiveTrigger,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,把它的 MinWindowWidth 设置成0\Nand set in this case the MinWindowWidth to zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,点击OK\Nand click OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来是状态 Tablet\NAnd then for Tablet,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把 MinWindowWidth 设成600\NI'm going to set it's MinWindowWidth I think to 600,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这其实是我随便输的数字啦\Nagain these are arbitrary numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以为自己的应用程序测试一下\Nyou would want to test this for your own application,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉这个没有绝对的标准\Nthere are no standards that I'm aware of,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该在某个阈值要使用\Nat certain break points you should be using
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,某个可视化状态。我觉得这些应该\Nthis versus that, I think this is something you get
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,由开发者你自己来决定\Nto determine on your own as the developer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，当窗口宽度大于等于 600 ，就会触发\NSo the MinWindowWidth 600, that will trigger
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,状态 Tablet，最后我们来设置状态 Desktop \Nhe Tablet state, and then finally the Desktop,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把它的最小值设为800\Nwe'll set it's minimum to 800.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里\NSo here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,800，好了\N800 great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,当处于状态 Desktop 时\NNow, whenever in Desktop mode,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想做什么呢，我要选择MessageTextBlock\Nwhat we want to do, I'm going to select the MessageTextBlock
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个对象和时间轴窗口里\Nhere in the Objects and Timeline window.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我要改变它的字体\NAnd then I'm going to change the font
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,大小改成54，我不记得我们刚开始那个数值了\Nto oh let's say 54, I forget what we chose originally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来我要设置状态 Tablet\NAnd then I'm going to go to the Tablet,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我要修改这个文本块\Nand then I'm going to change the TextBlock
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大小是36\Nto let's say 36.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,然后是状态 Phone\NAnd then I'm going to go to the Phone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,把它的字体大小改到16\Nand change it to like 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,继续\NAnd so now, let me go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,保存\Nsave what I have,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,运行\Nand then I'm going to run the application.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你看\NAnd you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这些变化就实现了\Nthat I was able to make those changes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,都是用这个工具实现的\Nusing this tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,再强调一遍，我个人是比较喜欢自己敲代码来实现的\NNow again, I would prefer to just type it in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,它确实创建了一个漂亮干净的 XAML，但是有些地方\NIt does create nice clean XAML, but there are some cases
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,比如处理颜色，处理笔刷\Nlike working with colors, and brushes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不喜欢它生成的 XAML\NI didn't like the XAML that it outputted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我更愿意自己手打\NThat's me just being a little snobby here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,当然你可以用这个工具来帮助自己\NBut otherwise you can use this tool to help you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,生成一些东西\Ngenerate these sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,当你关闭 Blend 的时候\NNow when you close down Blend,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就会返回到 Visual Studio\Nyou're going to come back into VisualStudio,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,它就会提示你，你是不是刚刚打开了一些窗口\Nit says hey, any windows that you had open,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,它们在 Visual Studio 之外的地方被改变了\Nthey changed out from under VisualStudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要重新加载吗\NDo you want to reload this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，我要重新加载，然后你就看到\NYes, I want to reload it and now you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的Visual States\NAll of the visual States
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还有触发器和 Setters\Nand the Triggers and the Setters
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,它们在 Visual Studio 都被更新了\Nare all updated here in VisualStudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢，这一个很简单的概念，很有用\NSo again, a very simple concept, very powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们如何使用这一功能\Nin how we can go about using this
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,根据不同的外形因素和分辨率方面\Nto style up our applications based on the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,样式化我们的应用程序\Nform factor and screen resolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,再说一遍，这是基本的概念\NAnd again, foundational concept for building real
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,用来创建一个真正的 UWP 应用程序\NUniversal Windows Platform applications.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要用到这个\NAnd so we're going to use this now
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在接下来的课程中\Nin the next lesson to actually
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,来创建更多实用的app\Ncreate a more realistic app,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,利用这些概念来改变布局\Nand utilize these concepts to change out the layout
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,基于可用的屏幕分辨率\Nbased on the available screen resolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:11:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好哒，我们就要进入激动人心的第二部分了\NAlright so stay tuned to exciting part two of this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,下节课见 (￣▽￣)"\Nin the very next lesson, thanks.
